cross: Paphiopedilum Hawaiian Illusion x Paphiopedilum Petula's Peacock

measurements.description: One flower and one bud on one 17-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal cream heavily overlaid mahogany, prominately veined darker mahogany, chartreuse proximally; synsepal cream overlaid mahogany proximal third and edges, veined darker mahogany, chartreuse proximally; petals burgundy, chartreuse proximally, hirsute edges; pouch burgundy; staminode chartreuse, burgundy distal edge; substance firm; texture glossy.
